# Capacitor native projects — generated by `cap add android/ios`. Commit them
# if you want platform-specific tweaks (icons, splash, AndroidManifest edits)
# under version control; otherwise re-generate per machine. Most teams DO
# commit them.
# android/
# ios/

# Capacitor build artifacts that are never source
